reviewText: I would love to be able to review this DVD, but I can't get it to play beyond the introduction. The other DVDs I ordered work fine, so it's not my machine. If anyone reads these, please let me know what to do.

Both DVDs give you a good workout. Both made me sweat. Both Leslie and Desi have a warm-up and a cool down. Even though this particular program (by Leslie) was made about 10 years ago, it is still very effective in giving you a good workout. Desi's workout is very thorough by involving cardio, toning, and flexibility.

I like the first two workouts on the 3 in 1, but the last one is a little hard to get into the postions. I love the Leslie Sansone. I like all her tapes and use her pilates regularly. This item came very fast and was new. Thanks so much!!
